subject: Diving (Sports Event)
Olympic Games (2012)
lead_paragraph: David Boudia of the United States was the last to make the semifinals of the 10-meter platform dive, but he ultimately beat out China’s Qiu Bo and Britain’s Tom Daley to win gold.
